  "detailed_description": "<h1>GAME OF MY FRIENDS</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/03b42bc98c1935b97e044e5e2e73d5b4.avif?t=1694986879\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Always look around you!<br><br><strong>Important point:</strong><br>➡ Multiplayer!<br>➡ 3 exclusive cards!<br>➡ 3 game modes!<br>➡ Offline mode<br>➡ Purchase of bombs and characters!<br>➡ Control in play with joystick!<br>➡ Addictive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.poster.avif?t=1694986879\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.webm?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.mp4?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of atypical characters and blow up as many enemies as possible. Single player or multiplayer, fight for wealth and get equipment that shows your power!<br>A large number of items improving your life count, bomb effectiveness and ingame performance will be available in the store to start a fight by giving your opponents no chance! <br><br><strong>Bonus effects in game:</strong><br>- Increased explosion range<br>- Increase in speed<br>- Increase in the number of bombs<br>- Life Bonus<br><br><strong>Will you be the best?</strong><br>Share your scores and battle photos in the Steam BOMBERX community!<br><br><strong>Let's do it! Let's do it!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/20ff32f73641b064b85e95ac2e306de8.poster.avif?t=1694986879\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/20ff32f73641b064b85e95ac2e306de8.webm?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/20ff32f73641b064b85e95ac2e306de8.mp4?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/03b42bc98c1935b97e044e5e2e73d5b4.avif?t=1694986879\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Always look around you!<br><br><strong>Important point:</strong><br>➡ Multiplayer!<br>➡ 3 exclusive cards!<br>➡ 3 game modes!<br>➡ Offline mode<br>➡ Purchase of bombs and characters!<br>➡ Control in play with joystick!<br>➡ Addictive!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.poster.avif?t=1694986879\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.webm?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/0621c5f0825a63978b8663d5a574c692.mp4?t=1694986879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take control of atypical characters and blow up as many enemies as possible. Single player or multiplayer, fight for wealth and get equipment that shows your power!<br>A large number of items improving your life count, bomb effectiveness and ingame performance will be available in the store to start a fight by giving your opponents no chance! <br><br><strong>Bonus effects in game:</strong><br>- Increased explosion range<br>- Increase in speed<br>- Increase in the number of bombs<br>- Life Bonus<br><br><strong>Will you be the best?</strong><br>Share your scores and battle photos in the Steam BOMBERX community!<br><br><strong>Let's do it! Let's do it!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1208900/extras/20ff32f73641b064b85e95ac2e306de8.p